<slide>
<title>Tagging a shard</title>

<example>
sh.addShardTag("shard0000", "ASIA");
sh.addShardTag("shard0001", "ASIA");
sh.addShardTag("shard0002", "ASIA");
sh.addShardTag("shard0003", "US");
sh.addShardTag("shard0004", "AUS");
</example>

<list>
	<bullet>The same tag can be used with multiple shards</bullet>
	<bullet>A shard can have more than one tag</bullet>
</list>
</slide>
